cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.CR

The paper deals with video analysis, organization, management, and control, which are all related to multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also proposes an approach to represent video information as video DNA sequences and apply bioinformatic algorithms, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), and deep learning (cs.DL). Additionally, the paper discusses the problem of detecting pirated content in YouTube, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR).
